title: Belgian Block: The Ideal Landscaping Accent for Coastal Homes
description: When it comes to coastal landscaping, certain challenges arise, primarily - the unpredictability of the elements. Island properties deal with a number of elements - the salty air, the wind, and nuisance flooding. The choices made in landscaping need to not only complement the natural beauty of the surroundings but also offer resilience to seasonal challenges. Enter the Belgian Block - a garden accent that blends aesthetics and function.

title: Coastal Erosion & Flooding Control
description: Owning a home on the 7 Mile Island offers soothing ocean sounds, salty breezes, and year-round relaxation. But it also presents unique challenges including rising water during storms and potential coastal erosion for shorefront properties. At Blue Quality Lawn Care, we specialize in providing sustainable landscaping services, with custom designs and maintenance plans for all types of properties.
